<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 40px 20px;
            color: white;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 3em;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-shadow: 0 2px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        }
        
        .main-card {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 40px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        
        .btn {
            padding: 16px 40px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 10px;
            text-decoration: none;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.4);
        }
        
        .btn:hover {
            transform: translateY(-3px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.6);
        }
        
        .content-section {
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }
        
        .content-section h2 {
            color: #667eea;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 2em;
            border-bottom: 3px solid #667eea;
            padding-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .content-section p {
            line-height: 1.8;
            color: #444;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 1.1em;
        }
        
        .features-list {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 30px;
        }
        
        .feature-item {
            background: #f8f9ff;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 15px;
            border-left: 5px solid #667eea;
        }
        
        .feature-item h3 {
            color: #667eea;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .warning-box {
            background: #fff3cd;
            border: 1px solid #ffeaa7;
            border-left: 5px solid #f39c12;
            padding: 25px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        
        .warning-box h3 {
            color: #d35400;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 40px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
            color: white;
            opacity: 0.8;
        }
        
        .actions {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .header h1 {
                font-size: 2em;
            }
            
            .main-card {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            
            .features-list {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>About YouTube Video Downloader</h1>
            <p>Learn more about our tool and how to use it responsibly</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="main-card">
            <div class="content-section">
                <h2>About This Tool</h2>
                <p>
                    YouTube Video Downloader is a free, open-source tool that allows you to download videos 
                    from YouTube in various formats and qualities. Our tool is designed to be fast, reliable, 
                    and easy to use.
                </p>
                <p>
                    This service runs entirely on your local machine - no data is sent to external servers 
                    during the download process. All processing happens on your computer, ensuring your 
                    privacy and security.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="content-section">
                <h2>Key Features</h2>
                <div class="features-list">
                    <div class="feature-item">
                        <h3>üé• Multiple Formats</h3>
                        <p>Download in MP4, WebM, 3GP, and other formats with various codec options.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-item">
                        <h3>üìä Quality Options</h3>
                        <p>Choose from multiple quality options including 144p, 360p, 720p, 1080p, and higher.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-item">
                        <h3>‚ö° Fast Downloads</h3>
                        <p>Utilizes direct streaming for maximum download speed.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-item">
                        <h3>üéµ Audio Extraction</h3>
                        <p>Download audio-only formats for music and podcasts.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-item">
                        <h3>üõ°Ô∏è Safe & Secure</h3>
                        <p>No malware, no viruses, and no user tracking.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-item">
                        <h3>üíØ Completely Free</h3>
                        <p>No registration, no subscriptions, no hidden fees.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="warning-box">
                <h3>‚ö†Ô∏è Important Legal Notice</h3>
                <p>
                    This tool is provided for educational purposes only. Users are responsible for complying 
                    with YouTube's Terms of Service and all applicable copyright laws.
                </p>
                <p>
                    <strong>Please note:</strong>
                </p>
                <ul style="margin-left: 20px; line-height: 1.8;">
                    <li>Only download videos that you have permission to download</li>
                    <li>Respect content creators' rights and copyrights</li>
                    <li>Do not distribute downloaded content without permission</li>
                    <li>This tool should be used for personal, non-commercial purposes only</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="content-section">
                <h2>How It Works</h2>
                <p>
                    1. Enter a YouTube URL in the homepage<br>
                    2. Our system analyzes the video and extracts available formats<br>
                    3. Select your preferred format and quality<br>
                    4. Click download to save the video to your device<br>
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="content-section">
                <h2>Technical Information</h2>
                <p>
                    This application is built with Node.js, Express.js, and uses yt-dlp for video information 
                    extraction. The download process uses direct streaming from YouTube's servers.
                </p>
                <p>
                    The source code is available for review and modification. This ensures transparency 
                    and allows users to verify that no malicious code is present.
                </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="actions">
                <a href="/" class="btn">
                    <span>üè†</span> Back to Home
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>¬© 2024 YouTube Video Downloader ‚Ä¢ Version 1.0.0</p>
            <p style="font-size: 0.9em; margin-top: 5px;">
                This tool is for educational purposes only. Use responsibly.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>